data.description: Located in "Brookside Glen South" of Tinley Park.  This 4 Bedroom, 2 Full baths an 2 half baths one first floor one in bath in finished basement.  Large office on 1st floor could easily be another bedroom. Property located on corner lot with lots of landscaping.  Full finished Basement with wet bar and huge recreation room, 3 Car Garage and 2nd floor windows replaced. Great family home offer lots of square footage for the money.  Paver brick patio leads to above ground pool and hot tub plus much more
